content.rendered:
The Study Industrial Side chair is a commercial grade classroom-look side chair perfect for industrial themes or those looking for a strong, care-free, stackable side chair.

Held in stock in a black steel frame with a riveted, dark oak veneered seat and backrest.

Stackable up to 4 high.
